vdbi-vim
========

Database client for Vim.

Usage:
------

```
:VDBI
```


Requirements:
-------------

* vim webapi-vim https://github.com/mattn/webapi-vim
* perl Plack

Install:
--------

```
$ cd ~/.vim/bundle
$ git clone https://github.com/mattn/webapi-vim
```

```
$ cpanm DBI Plack RPC::XML RPC::XML::ParserFactory
```

